# Crossword repository workflow

- Treat `puzzles/*/puzzle.json` as canonical. Never edit an export as source.
- Validate every changed puzzle with `uv run crossword-validate <path>`.
- Regenerate its `web/puzzles/*.puz` file after changing a canonical puzzle.
- Keep `web/puzzles.json` synchronized with bundled puzzle assets.
- Write construction candidates only to ignored `scratch/`.
- Never commit contact details, submission forms, private PDFs, caches, or raw
  construction attempts.
- Run `uv run pytest` before committing.
- Review the complete staged file list for puzzle spoilers and sensitive data.
